Package com.da.antiphish.tasks

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BlacklistTask
    This task checks if the given URL is in blacklist or not.
    DomainAgeTask
    This task checks if the domain age of the URL is less than or equal to a specified threshold or not.
    DotsTask
    This task checks if the number of dots in the URL is greater than a specified threshold or not.
    EmptyLinksTask
    This task checks if the rate of empty links of the website is greater than a specified threshold or not.
    FormTagsTask
    This task checks if the website contains bad forms or not.
    FrameTask
    This task checks if the website contains suspicious frames or not.
    InputTagsTask
    This task checks if the website contains input fields ( tags) or not.
    IPAddressTask
    This task checks if the URL of the website contains an IPv4 or IPv6 address or not.
    MetaTagsTask
    This task checks if the meta tags contain suspicious keywords/contents from meta list (meta_content.json) or not.
    NoLinksBodyTask
    This task checks if the website contains input fields ( tags) but no links.
    NonmatchingUrlTask
    This task checks if the website contains at least one link ( tag) where the text of the link is an URL which is different to the URL in the href-attribute.
    OnlyScriptTask
    This task checks if the body of the website is empty but there are script tags available.
    PlaintextContentTask
    This task checks if the plaintext of the website contain suspicious keywords/contents from content list (phishing_content.json).
    PunctuationTask
    This task checks if the number of punctuations (. !
    SuspiciousLinksTask
    This task checks if the website contains suspicius links.
    SuspiciousScriptContentTask
    This task checks if the script tags of the website contain suspicious keywords/contents from script list (script_content.json).
    SuspiciousUrlTask
    This task checks if the URL of the website is suspicious.
    Task
    Task is the abstract base class for all single analysis steps and provides only one single abstract method getResult().
    TaskResult
    ResultObject represents the result of an analysis task and includes the following information: taskName: the name of the analysis task category: the category of the analysis task score: the final score of the analysis task addInfo: additional information of specific tasks, only for analysis purposes
    TitleTask
    This task checks if at least one word of the title of the website also occurs in the domain name of the URL.
    WebsiteIdentityTask
    This task checks if the identity of the website has a relationship to the domain of the URL.
    WhitelistTask
    This task checks if the given URL is in whitelist or not.
